name: Scathach Skadi 12Outfits 斯卡哈·斯卡蒂 12套外观 (Fate Grand Order)
description:
このLoRAモデルを使用して画像を生成し、インターネット上で公開する際に、他の人が簡単に見つけられるように、原作者とモデルのウェブサイトを明記していただけると、非常に感謝いたします

当您使用此LoRA模型生成图片并发布在网上，希望可以注明一下该模型的原网址和作者方便他人查找，谢谢

When you use this LoRA model to generate images and publish them online, I would greatly appreciate it if you could indicate the original website and author of the model to make it easier for others to find.

-

LoRa of Scathach=Skadi from FGO, works between 0.7-0.9

FGO斯卡哈·斯卡蒂的模型，推荐权重0.7-0.9

support 12 sets of outfit, 11 official and 1 from Orangemaru's hentai fanart

支持12套外观, 11套官方外观和1套Orangemaru女仆同人小黄本的外观

-

Caster1: DefaultOutfit, C1

Caster3: CasterFinalOutfit, C3

OrangeMaru's Maid Hentai Fanart女仆同人本: maid, Oranmaru

SwimsuitRuler2: R2, 2ndROutfit, glasses

SwimsuitRuler3: R3, 3rdSwimsuit, veil

SwimsuitRulerFinal: R4, FinalSwimsuit

-CE概念礼装-

Heroic Spirit Travel Journal英灵纪行：HSTO, TripOutfit
